OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy at times with variable
OL,6,Fcloud for much of the period, staying
OL,7,Fmostly dry. Temperatures likely above
OL,8,Faverage, becoming very warm or hot in
OL,9,Fplaces.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and settled evening,
OL,12,Fremaining cloudy for the most. The
OL,13,Fwind will ease slightly, but remaining
OL,14,Fbreezy along the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FCloudy to start, with some
OL,17,Flonger sunny periods developing during
OL,18,Fthe afternoon as temperatures become
OL,19,Fvery warm or hot in places. Winds
OL,20,Flight but breezy along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
